      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\cognitive-taxonomy-site\\index.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <!DOCTYPE html>\n2: <html lang=\"en\">\n3: <head>\n4: <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n5: <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n6: <meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#0f0f0f\">\n7: <meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"dark\">\n8: <title>Cognitive Taxonomy Protocol — Rewire How You Read Code</title>\n9: <meta name=\"description\" content=\"A five-colour taxonomy that rewires how you read code. From line-by-line scanning to instant pattern recognition.\">\n10: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n11: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n12: <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n13: <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/style.css\">\n14: </head>\n15: <body>\n16: \n17: <!-- Skip to content (accessibility) -->\n18: <a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"skip-link\">Skip to main content</a>\n19: \n20: <!-- ── Navigation ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n21: <nav class=\"nav\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\">\n22:   <div class=\"nav-inner\">\n23:     <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"nav-brand\">\n24:       <span class=\"nav-logo\">\n25:         <span class=\"nav-logo-dot\" style=\"background:var(--blue)\"></span>\n26:         <span class=\"nav-logo-dot\" style=\"background:var(--green)\"></span>\n27:         <span class=\"nav-logo-dot\" style=\"background:var(--orange)\"></span>\n28:         <span class=\"nav-logo-dot\" style=\"background:var(--red)\"></span>\n29:         <span class=\"nav-logo-dot\" style=\"background:var(--purple)\"></span>\n30:       </span>\n31:       CTP\n32:     </a>\n33:     <button class=\"nav-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\">\n34:       <span></span><span></span><span></span>\n35:     </button>\n36:     <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n37:       <li><a href=\"index.html\" class=\"nav-link active\">Home</a></li>\n38:       <li><a href=\"about.html\" class=\"nav-link\">About</a></li>\n39:       <li><a href=\"install.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Install</a></li>\n40:       <li><a href=\"demo.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Demo</a></li>\n41:       <li><a href=\"wiki.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Wiki</a></li>\n42:       <li><a href=\"install.html\" class=\"nav-cta\">Get Started</a></li>\n43:     </ul>\n44:   </div>\n45: </nav>\n46: \n47: <main id=\"main-content\">\n48: <!-- ── Hero ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n49: <section class=\"hero\">\n50:   <div class=\"container\">\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 230. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>",
