      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.gemini\\antigravity\\scratch\\Prolector-Google-AI-Studio-prototypee\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <div align=\"center\">\n2: <img width=\"1200\" height=\"475\" alt=\"GHBanner\" src=\"https://ai.google.dev/static/site-assets/images/share-ais-513315318.png\" />\n3: </div>\n4: \n5: # Run and deploy your AI Studio app\n6: \n7: This contains everything you need to run your app locally.\n8: \n9: View your app in AI Studio: https://ai.studio/apps/316cfa2f-ec6e-4d92-a59e-ddc39ee90463\n10: \n11: ## Run Locally\n12: \n13: **Prerequisites:**  Node.js\n14: \n15: \n16: 1. Install dependencies:\n17:    `npm install`\n18: 2. Set the `GEMINI_API_KEY` in [.env.local](.env.local) to your Gemini API key\n19: 3. Run the app:\n20:    `npm run dev`\n\n(End of file - total 20 lines)\n</content>",
