    {
      "type": "answer",
      "text": "## ProLector — Your Replit Program Explained\n\nYou have **two versions** of ProLector on your machine:\n\n---\n\n### **1. ProLector v2.0 (Main Version)**\n**Location:** `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.gemini\\antigravity\\scratch\\prolector-yourvoice-perfected\\`\n\n**What it is:** A **local-first video production workstation for educators** — a browser-based alternative to tools like OBS, Camtasia, or ScreenFlow.\n\n#### Core Features:\n\n| Feature | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Teleprompter** | Word-level scrub editor with WPM-locked pacing, mirror mode for confidence monitors |\n| **Voice Cloning (SyllabusMirror)** | Routes sentences through Kokoro-82M TTS with sliding 8-second window, CPU feedback loop |\n| **Studio (Video Editor)** | Drop iPhone `.mov`/`.mp4`, demux with MP4Box, decode via WebCodecs, edit non-destructively against JSON EDL |\n| **EDL (Edit Decision List)** | Every cut/split/overlay stored as 2KB JSON — not 500MB MP4 |\n\n#### Tech Stack:\n- **Frontend:** React 19 + TanStack Router + Tailwind CSS 4\n- **Video:** Remotion (React-based video renderer) + MP4Box + WebCodecs\n- **TTS:** Kokoro-82M (runs in browser, sub-100ms on CPU)\n- **State:** Zustand + React Query\n- **Build:** Vite 7 + TypeScript\n\n#### Pricing Tiers (SaaS Model):\n| Tier | Price | Audience |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| Standard | $4.20/mo | Individual Educator |\n| Plus | $9.60/mo | Active Course Creator |\n| Pro | $15.60/mo | Production House |\n| Select | $21.00/mo | Enterprise Academy |\n\n---\n\n### **2. ProLector Google AI Studio Prototype**\n**Location:** `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.gemini\\antigravity\\scratch\\Prolector-Google-AI-Studio-prototypee\\`\n\n**What it is:** An earlier prototype with 5 tabs:\n1. **Studio** — Semantic scene workstation\n2. **Library** — Ebook reader with lead capture\n3. **Teleprompter** — Remotion timeline studio\n4. **EDL Sandbox** — Edit decision list editor\n5. **Settings** — Lead management portal\n\n---\n\n### **Key Innovation: \"Your Voice Perfected\"**\n\nThe core idea is **voice cloning for educators**:\n- Clone your voice using F5-TTS, Chatterbox-Turbo, or Kokoro-82M\n- Condition it with **regional vocal archetypes** (as you mentioned)\n- Practice sounding like a local before presenting\n- Edit video non-destructively using JSON EDLs\n- Export without re-encoding (re-mux only)\n\nThe teleprompter routes sentences across different TTS engines based on a live CPU feedback loop — short sentences go to Kokoro q4 (low latency), long sentences go to Kokoro q8 (quality), with browser SpeechSynthesis as fallback.",
      "timestamp": 1781544464354
    },
