      "text": "Now I have a complete picture. Let me implement all the features. I'll create:\n\n1. **Prosody data model** - Extend Token type with prosody data (pitch, stress, coarticulation)\n2. **ProsodyVisualizer component** - Render pitch contours, stress markers, coarticulation bridges\n3. **useTriage hook** - Stumble marker tracking\n4. **StumblePlaylist component** - Auto-generated loop ranges\n5. **useRecording hook** - MediaRecorder + AudioContext alignment\n6. **ABContrast component** - Side-by-side playback\n7. **PunchInEditor component** - Non-destructive cross-fade stitching\n\n\n8. **Integrate everything** - Update teleprompter.tsx to wire all these pieces together\n\nStarting with the core data model and working outward...",
