      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Now let me do the big integration. I need to:\n1. Import all new hooks and components\n2. Add state for prosody, triage, recording, AB contrast, punch-in\n3. Add keyboard shortcut for Space to flag stumbles (when not playing)\n4. Add the prosody computation logic\n5. Wire everything together\n\nLet me write the updated teleprompter.tsx.",
