      "type": "answer",
      "text": "All done. Here's what was built and pushed to `andiekobbietks/prolector-yourvoice-perfected`:\n\n## New Features (5 files, 1,622 lines added)\n\n| Feature | Files | What It Does |\n|---------|-------|-------------|\n| **Visual Prosody** | `prosody.ts`, `ProsodyVisualizer.tsx` | F0 pitch contour sparklines, stress badges (●/○/·), vowel compression ratios (full/compressed/reduced/schwa), coarticulation bridge icons (→r, ↻, ⊘, ≈, ɾ) with tooltips explaining each linguistic rule |\n| **Hotkey Triage** | `use-triage.ts` | Spacebar flags stumbles during playback — AudioContext.currentTime aligned, persisted to localStorage. No menus, no classification, pure System 1 reflex |\n| **Stumble Playlist** | `StumblePlaylist.tsx` | Auto-generates 1.5s-before / 2s-after loop clips from flagged markers. Play sequentially, set as loop range, or remove |\n| **A/B Contrast** | `ABContrast.tsx` | Toggle between your recording and AI reference. Alternating mode switches every 3s. Waveform visualization with playhead |\n| **Punch-In Editor** | `PunchInEditor.tsx` | Set in/out points, re-record just that section. Non-destructive with 150ms cross-fade boundaries |\n\n## Updated Teleprompter\n\n- **Side panel** now has 4 tabs: Voice, Stumbles (shows count badge), Compare, Punch-In\n- **Keyboard shortcuts**: `P` = prosody overlays, `M` = mirror, `Space` = flag during playback / play-pause when stopped\n- **TranscriptStage** highlights flagged words in red when near a triage marker\n\n## What's Left\n\nThe only remaining item is copy-level: reframing \"Clone My Voice\" as \"Auditory Feedforward Training\" on the landing page with science-backed tooltips. That's a marketing/copy change, not code. Want me to do it?",
