    {
      "type": "answer",
      "text": "All 8 tasks complete. Pushed to `andiekobbietks/prolector-yourvoice-perfected`.\n\n## What's on the landing page now\n\n**Surface layer** (everyone gets this):\n- Headline: *\"Hear yourself speak — then hear yourself improved.\"*\n- 3-step explainer: Record → Perfect → Brain absorbs\n- Plain language: *\"Your brain absorbs the correction faster because it sounds like you, not a stranger.\"*\n\n**Deep layer** (click \"What's the science behind this?\"):\n- Feedforward Self-Modeling (Dowrick 1991–2012)\n- Own-Voice Advantage (auditory cortex latency)\n- Hebbian Myelination (repetition insulates nerve fibres)\n- Dual-Stream Processing (Hickok & Poeppel 2007)\n- Full references at the bottom\n\n**Updated copy throughout:**\n- Pricing tier: \"Voice Clone Training (F5-TTS)\" instead of \"F5-TTS Vocal Mirror\"\n- EDL example: `feedforward_voice_clone.wav`\n- OG description: \"Auditory feedforward training with voice cloning\"\n- Hero: \"Train your voice. Polish your delivery.\"",
