      "text": "Now let me add Deepgram Aura as a 6th engine. I need to:\n1. Add \"deepgram-aura\" to EngineId\n2. Add it to the engines record\n3. Add a synthesize case for it\n4. Add it to the pickEngine routing\n5. Add a loader for it\n\nLet me also check how the experimental engines are loaded to follow the same pattern.",
