uring playback)</li>\n729:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">R</kbd> · reset</li>\n730:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">↑ ↓</kbd> · ± 5 WPM</li>\n731:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">P</kbd> · toggle prosody overlays</li>\n732:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">M</kbd> · toggle mirror</li>\n733:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">click</kbd> · scrub to word</li>\n734:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">shift+click</kbd> · set loop range</li>\n735:                       <li><kbd className=\"text-foreground\">right-click</kbd> · re-synth menu</li>\n736:                     </ul>\n737:                   </section>\n738:                 </>\n739:               )}\n740: \n741:               {/* Stumbles tab */}\n742:               {activeTab === \"stumbles\" && (\n743:                 <section>\n744:                   <StumblePlaylist\n745:                     markers={markers}\n746:                     tokens={tokens}\n747:                     currentMs={currentMs}\n748:                     onSelectRange={handleSelectStumbleRange}\n749:                     onPlayRange={handlePlayStumbleRange}\n750:                     onRemoveMarker={removeMarker}\n751:                     onClearAll={clearMarkers}\n752:                   />\n753:                 </section>\n754:               )}\n755: \n756:               {/* Compare tab */}\n757:               {activeTab === \"compare\" && (\n758:                 <section>\n759:                   <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-primary mb-3\">\n\n(Showing lines 700-759 of 834. Use offset=760 to continue.)\n</content>",
