      "type": "user-query",
      "text": "No explanation of what \"prosody\" means on first visit\nNo onboarding flow for non-technical users\nNo guidance on what WPM to start with\nNo progress tracking across sessions\nNo teacher/classroom mode\nNo non-English language support\nNo dialect selection beyond the 6 Kokoro voices\n\nupdate with all this to ensure its a solid product then",
