      "tool": "bash",
      "code": "{\"command\": \"git commit -m \\\"feat: fill 7 product gaps \\u2014 onboarding, prosody explainer, WPM guide, progress, classroom, language, voices\\n\\n1. Prosody Explainer \\u2014 Dismissible banner on first visit with plain-language\\n   definition + expandable Collapsible for technical detail (stress, rhythm,\\n   intonation examples)\\n\\n2. Onboarding Flow \\u2014 4-step wizard: Welcome, What is Prosody, How It Works,\\n   Personalize (native language selector 11 languages, CEFR level A2-C2,\\n   WPM recommendation). Persists to localStorage\\n\\n3. WPM Guidance \\u2014 Visual scale with 5 CEFR levels, recommended WPM ranges,\\n   real-world benchmarks (TED 110-130, BBC 150-160, etc). Click to set WPM\\n\\n4. Progress Tracking \\u2014 session-stats.ts records every session >5s: date,\\n   duration, WPM, words spoken, stumble count. Calculates streak, average\\n   WPM, total words. ProgressDashboard component shows stats + history\\n\\n5. Teacher/Classroom Mode \\u2014 /classroom route with student table, class\\n   stats (active today, avg WPM), assignable script library, level badges.\\n   Demo data for preview\\n\\n6. Non-English Language Support \\u2014 Onboarding asks native language (11 options):\\n   EN, IT, ES, FR, DE, PT, JA, ZH, KO, AR, HI. Stored for future\\n   localisation\\n\\n7. Expanded Voices \\u2014 6 Kokoro voices + 8 Deepgram Aura voices (asteria,\\n   luna, stella, athena, hera, orion, arcas, perseus). Total: 14 voice\\n   options\\n\\nAlso: Fixed FloatingPlayer TypeScript 5.8 compat, added session recording\\non teleprompter stop, added Progress and WPM tabs to side panel\\\"\", \"description\": \"Commit all 7 product gap fixes\", \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\.gemini\\\\antigravity\\\\scratch\\\\prolector-yourvoice-perfected\"}",
