      "text": "All 7 gaps filled. Pushed to `andiekobbietks/prolector-yourvoice-perfected`.\n\n## What's new\n\n| Gap | What was built | Where |\n|---|---|---|\n| **No prosody explainer** | Dismissible banner with plain-language definition + expandable Collapsible for stress/rhythm/intonation examples | Landing page top |\n| **No onboarding** | 4-step wizard: Welcome → What is Prosody → How It Works → Personalize (language + level + WPM recommendation) | First visit modal |\n| **No WPM guidance** | Visual scale with 5 CEFR levels, real-world benchmarks (TED, BBC, Audiobook, etc), click to set WPM | Teleprompter side panel → WPM tab |\n| **No progress tracking** | Auto-records sessions >5s: streak, total practice time, avg WPM, words spoken, session history | Teleprompter side panel → Progress tab |\n| **No teacher mode** | `/classroom` route: student table, class stats, level badges, assignable script library | Nav → Classroom |\n| **No non-English support** | 11 native language options in onboarding: EN, IT, ES, FR, DE, PT, JA, ZH, KO, AR, HI | Onboarding step 3 |\n| **Limited voices** | 6 Kokoro + 8 Deepgram Aura = **14 voice options** total | Teleprompter + Deepgram config |\n\n**Bonus:** Fixed FloatingPlayer TypeScript 5.8 compat, added session recording on teleprompter stop.",
